  "texts": [
    "37 have performed a public online survey and interviews to discover attributes that could influence the privacy perceptions of the users in Internet of Things (IoT) environments.",
    "Though diverse participants recognized the privacy threats in the IoT, this work discovered that a large amount of users would still decide to have a provided IoT service if they discovered it helpful.",
    "This work summarized by validating and showcasing the participant's qualitative comments ad recommended possible outcomes for the recognized problems.",
    "Problem statementHuman motion intention prediction (MIP) has become a significant tool in multiple sectors, including robotics, healthcare, and others.",
    "In the fast-moving world, a portable and wearable sensor system has been introduced, which is self-powered to maximize the complexity of human-machine interaction."
  ]
